        <Parent_String>defensive walls [300002485], defensive walls and defensive wall components [300079573], fortification elements [300003687], architectural elements by building type [300078071], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
